	<div class="container">
		<div class="project-hero__content">
			
			<h1 class="project-hero__title">All too often, California’s default mental institutions are now jails and prisons</h1>

			
						<p class="project-hero__intro">In the past five years, the number of people in California deemed incompetent to stand trial and referred by a judge to state hospitals for treatment has soared—but there are nowhere near enough psychiatric beds to accommodate them.</p>
			
							<div class="project-hero__caption">

									</div>
					</div>
	</div>
</div>

